PrecisRe-appointment of RON KUBAN of Edmonton, Alberta, who is not an officer or non-commissioned member of the Canadian Forces, nor an employee of the Department of National Defence, as a part-time member of the Military Police Complaints Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years.
